sentences: Jon Micah Sumrall (born October 13, 1980) is an American musical performer and lead vocalist of the Christian rock band Kutless.
Sumrall has been a member of Kutless since he started the band with James Mead and Ryan Shrout in 2001.
He released, Faith & Family, with BEC Recordings, in 2015.
He has been the lead vocalist for the Christian rock band Kutless, since its inception in 1999.
